messages.content:
Barselius took some equipment. and headed to the field. He wasn't tired, and. it was time to see what he was made of off, He began training his speed. And when his legs started to hurt, and he fell. He got up. and started running again, he repeated the process untill his legs couldn't stand anymore. whereas he started working on his arms. 
"i need. To, Be , the best" he said under his breath

after a while. he stands back up, his legs don't want to work anymore. He starts to punch the air the pressure seemed to cut the clouds ahead. he kept going and going. untill his body wanted to shut off "i'm not... Giving up" he says between huffs *i need to be the strongest*
After a few more rounds. he collapsed on his back while doing situps. he's awaken but, can't move a muscle

Smaller footsteps crunch the grass underneath them, as a figure approaches Barselius, careful to keep their tail above the flammable plant life 
“**Oh geez, Are you alright?**”
"N-no" he musters laying on his back
“**Oh no!”** Caelo frets, “**W-We gotta get you someplace safer then**!” The mun quickly looks over the situation, *woah, he’s big!* .
"Chill" he coughs trying to sit up "i'm just tired" he is sitting up. kinda
“**Really? You seem very injured**....” he sat next to him, “**or at least kinda lonely.”**
"second option" he chuckled "Just, overexercised"

**” I see....well....I’ll stay with you until you feel less lonely, yeah!”** He proudly states, pumping his fist in the air. “**Oh, I’m Caelo by the way mister!”** the mun gave a big smile, turning his head to him.
"Name's barselius!" he turns his head to him smiling "Damn you're small"
“Yeah...I’m kinda small, but you’re also.,... like *super* huge.” He sheepishly laughs, gesturing to the large size difference between them.
"Fair point" he says noticing it "I was just warming up."

“Warm up? Wow.....your normal routine must be really extreme if the *warmup* left you like....*that*.....” he winces at the thought of it....if he himself tried that....he’d for sure lose his other arm...
"Hey. i just try to workout" he smiles "also. buddy what happened to... yknow, your arm?"
“Huh? Oh! I uh, was born without it, guess I’m a little defective than most muns but that won’t stop me! Just makes me more determined!”
"Hey" his face glows almost "Me too!" he shows the metal arms "Prosthetics... But i'm defective in another way"
((is barselius gonna be the dad to kalo too?

His eyes widen in excitement as he sprung up “**WO-AH!** They look sooo cool! Can you shoot lasers out of them?! O-Or punch super hard?!” He’s practically bouncing in place. 
((Djdjfk probably))
"see those clouds" he points the parted clouds on the sky "i did that" he smiles "I also can do a bunch of other stuff"
((barselius when he sees someone younger than him: *oh boy dad time*

Caleo gives a gasp of amazement, looking up, “You did **That!?!** you must be super powerful!! What other stuff?!” 
((It’s the dad instinct))
"like" he turns his arm into a piston puncher "this" then into a jet engine "this, How about you?"

“WOW! You can transform it?! That’s so awesome!” The mun then looks back up at Barselius, “uh.......Me? Um...I have a stand...but I usually only use its arm, I....don’t really like using its ability....” he rubs the back of his neck.
"what does it do?" he looks at him "well. yknow, for a plasma. i'm not the top of the box either. I don't even have powers"

“Well....if I’m angry...I breathe fire, more angry I am the hotter the fire...I think the hottest I’ve gotten is.....uhhhhhh” he racks his brain, kinda zoning out, before snapping his fingers, “1,400 °C! So uh....bright yellow! I can’t...control it though....so I try not to get angry.” His head looks to the side, thinking of a way to change the subject...
“....Weeelllll, I still think you’re the *coolest* Plasma any other day.”

"hey you get stronger as you get angrier too?" barselius lightly punches Caleo arm "Me too! but i work on a diferent way" feeling well enough to stand. he does. at his twenty two feet at height "God you're tiny, Also. about being the coolest plasma, Comeon kiddo. i'm not even on the top ten"

“Oh woah! I’m not even as tall as your knees! Wait...” he summoned Imagine dragons, who’s fairly taller than its user, and climbs up to sit on one of its heads, “There!” He beamed 
“Yeah but those Plasma are either Creepy, weird, evil, or all three. I mean...those two plasma ladies at the temple seemed nice but....they didn’t seem that cool...”
“I’d take you over all those Plasma!”

he gets a ping on his tesseract "Oh shit" he sighs "hey, kid. i need to open up my gym. you can come to see it if you want. but i am already about an hour behind schedule." he takes out a card out of his pocket "here. this is the location number blahblahblah. just come if you want to workout at a slower pace" he said before heading to #barselius-gym
He grabs the card curiously, “O-Ok!” Caelo waves goodbye to his new friend, giving a small smile.
he backs down. "You know what.... i can stay!"
“Huh? You sure?”
"Y-yeah" *dad instincts engage*
“Oh! Cool!” He still slipped the card into his pouch, “...Sooo, Do you have any friends?” He piped up,
"only one" he sighs "well. two now" he chuckles
“Really? Who are they?” His interest is now peeked,
"Well. there's ombrage, She's like. What you would call a daughter?" he says smiling like an idiot "And. uh,  Well the other one WAS my friend. his name is polaris"
“Oh! She seems nice! Wonder if I could meet her.....” the other name cause his eyes to light up, “wait.....You friends with **Polaris**!?!” He (almost) shouts,
"Was" he corrects caleo
“O-oh, did something....happen?” His smile dropped.
"I Guess he kinda pulled my heartstrings a little" he sighs "it's fine though"
"it's fine tho. all water under the bridge. i just don't like him *that* much"
“I see.....” He mumbles
"it's alright. More my fault than anything." he sighs "Either way. why you so surprised? he's kind of a big thing on the rebelion side"

“Well I kinda look up to him....and hearing that my new friend knew him, was cool!”
“I don’t....really know much about the rebellion stuff....I just knew Polaris as Jotaro’s Mun..I wish to be as strong as him someday to protect my friends......or at least as smart...”

"Oh comeon, smartness is WAY too overated" he kneels to be close to kaleo height "Listen. To be strong. you can't look UP to noone. You have to work. pull your own weight and more. So someday you can be looked up to" he smiles "you know what. here" he takes off his mask. the six eyes one
The mun looked in awe, at Barselius’s speech, his fiery tail swaying, though a expression of confusion fades in at the removal of the mask, “huh..?”

His face is extremely scarred "Here. It's a tad too big" he chuckles "but, with time, it will fit" he hands the mask over "take it as a gift! you know. as. a way for you to keep training!" he smiles "And, if you want i can be your professor... Not that i'm good at those things"

“R-Really?! For me?....Y-You’re....giving me this?” He gently clutches the mask, tears pricking the corner of his eyes, “Thank you....**Thank youthankyouthankyouthsnkyouthankyou!”** he shakily repeated.
"It's just a mask!" he chuckled at caleo "It does do this" he presses a button on the side of the mask and the eyes glow up "good for scaring people"
“Y-Yeah, but....no-one has ever given me something.....especially something this cool!” He grinned, wiping some of the tears that managed to drip down his cheek,
"Well. there's always a first time for everything" he smiled "Plus. you did say you wanted to be stronger right?"
“Right.”
"Well. How old are you?"
"Welp. then, The best time to start training would be a thousand years ago. second best is now"
“O-K!” He proudly says
"You want to? Because if you say yess i can promise you you're gonna be one of the strongest muns there can be"
“**Y-Yes! I do!**”
"Well then" he gets up "Let's start shal we?"
“Uh huh!” He mimics him, scrambling to get up.
"first. show me what you got" he motions with his hand "like. what can you do?"
“Right!.” Caelo takes haste in darting around behind Barselius and delivering a punch to the lower part of his leg,

his leg doesn't move "NICE!" he claps "You managed to make me feel the punch. that's quite hard" he smiles proudly "But. less straight on punch. more tactics. Tell me. If you were to *actually* fight me. What would you do"

He looks down, in thought, “Hmm....well I’d focus more on dodging your attacks, tiring you out, since only a few of your punches would definitely do me in......but I also should land hits of my own, make them count, try and find your ‘Achilles heel’...can’t rely on my stand otherwise there’d be major collateral damage..” his voice mumbles

"Allow me to tell you. Colateral damage is just Extra damage done to diferent areas" he says walking arround  "If. i punch something. most likely the sheer Air pressure of my punch would cause colateral damage." he looks arround "What you need to know how to do is. Focus the colateral damage. on places where it would be optimal. Like. If you are agains one single opnent. Wou could try making the ground aflame. unless they themselves can fly. They are... Well, Toast"
“R-Right....” his gaze followed the plasma as he moved,
"so, you have to atack. with all your might. else the fighti you're fighting is already lost"
“Uh huh.” He nods,
"so. can you try using your stand, just so i know what it does"
“I’ll try....” he breathes in, and focuses on anger, though only few sparks of dull red flame come out.
"hm. So, you have to be. angry?"
“Yeah...”
"That might not be optimal..." he sighs "Welp. Then what you do is. Get strong" he flexes "To be as strong as me"
He nodded, determined, “right! I will!” Caelo tried to strike a pose similar to Barselius, holding the mask up to his face, “Gggrawr!”
"adorable!" he chuckles "Well. wanna learn a secret kiddo?"
“Yeah!” He early looks up.
"it's all in the legs" he points at his "You can't fight if you get tired. so. What you say we do a little jog back to town?"
“O-Ok!” Goodness he is very excited, practically bobbing with enthusiasm
(( barselius gon take him to either the mcdonalds or an ice cream shop
((D’awwwww :aww: ))
They head to the #ice-cream-place
